eventText: Andrea asks on Friday, 9 Feb, if baby default can be changed from server update.
Sambhaji replied back that splash screen can be changed from server update.
Sambhaji sends the last app backup to Shrinath
Pranav makes the changes in splash screen and sends for approval to Andrea.
Andrea sends a confirmation on the splash screen.
Andrea sends an email that she will complete the changes today.
Andrea has completed her changes on CMS. Sambhaji requests Gaurav to send the data and Pranav to send the baby default.
Sambhaji gave a decision to Piyush to replace the data on both the production and test paths. Some issue with the online app and previous server updates.
AGO app is uploaded on testflight for internal testing in BBI.
Sambhaji sends the invitation to Andrea again.
Andrea tells to change the server update popup also. Shrinath and Piyush already made the changes.
Andrea is fine with the server update popup text from Nathalie.
Sambhaji asks for final server update approval to Andrea.
Andrea has given her approval for the final server update.
Sambhaji approves the server update of AGO app. The Android version is crashing sometimes on notes and bookmarks.
Server update is pushed in the online app by Shrinath and Piyush.
